Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會怎麼樣 你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,會成為這些魔神族的餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,神千斬
